    "With Falcon 7B and MPT-7B, two strong competitors joined the field in June 2023 with 40% and 40.9% correct answers.",
    "They both rely on own pretrained models and can therefore be used commercially, in contrast to the LLaMA-based alternatives.",
    "Finally, WizardLM took the lead in the 7B parameter models with 47.3% correct answers.The finetuned T5 family of models performed rather good in our tests (see table 2).",
    "Scores reach from 37.3% to 44.5% of Flan-T5.",
    "However, they still perform slightly worse than the smallermodels Alpaca 7B and WizardLM 7B."
